Oddcast,offers,a,set,of,APIs,that,allow,developers,to,add,tools,to,enterprise,level,platforms,to,enhance,the,user,s,engagement,with,their,media,The,Oddcast,AV,Capture,Module,allows,a,user,to,capture,the,audio,and,video,of,any,event,that,that,takes,place,on,a,webcam,or,on,a,screen,within,a,Flash,application,and,packages,the,video,up,in,an,easy,to,share,MP,or,FLV,format,This,Actionscript,API,allows,the,application,to,customize,cropping,area,dimensions,and,output,type,of,the,videos